  <div class="about-body">
    <div class="content-wrap">

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>LWS Media Network was born out of a simple but powerful belief — that the most important stories in the world are often the ones nobody is telling. Founded by Sasha Gaye Hemmings, a solo entrepreneur and independent journalist based in Miami, Florida, LWS Media Network is the media arm of Geor De Mer LLC and a natural extension of a brand built on purpose, creativity, and impact.</p>
        <p>The platform launched with a single cover story — a profile of Samara, a nine-year-old who inspired a global educational platform, a YouTube channel, and a legacy of intentional building. That story set the tone for everything that followed: real people, real journeys, and real impact told without compromise.</p>
        <div class="about-quote">
          <p>"I wanted to build a media platform that actually reflects the world as it is — full of incredible people doing extraordinary things that never make the front page."</p>
          <cite>— Sasha Gaye Hemmings, Founder & Editor in Chief</cite>
        </div>
        <p>From young creators changing their communities to solo founders building global products, from underreported global crises to unfiltered commentary on world events — LWS Media Network covers it all with integrity, depth, and a distinct voice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section">
        <h2>Meet the Founder</h2>
        <div class="founder-card">
          <div class="founder-avatar"><i class="ti ti-user"></i></div>
          <div>
            <p class="founder-name">Sasha Gaye Hemmings</p>
            <p class="founder-title">Founder & Editor in Chief</p>
            <p class="founder-bio">Sasha Gaye Hemmings is a Jamaican-born entrepreneur, independent journalist, and mother based in Miami, Florida. She is the founder and sole operator of Geor De Mer LLC — a lifestyle and media company with three distinct verticals: Learning With Samara (edtech), LWS Media Network (media), and Geor De Mer (lifestyle e-commerce).</p>
            <p class="founder-bio" style="margin-top:10px;">With a background in independent journalism and a passion for stories that challenge the mainstream narrative, Sasha built LWS Media Network as a platform where every voice matters — especially the ones the world tends to overlook.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

